o explained, =E2=80=9Cperformance marketing is just the ability to convert =
the work we=E2=80=99ve done with our product and aspirational brand.=E2=80=
=9D=C2=A0
The whole strategy is a long-term bet on the product=E2=80=99s ability to h=
elp people sleep better, and the belief that it will show up in the numbers=
