r hardware company.=C2=A0
It=E2=80=99s brought in more money over the past twelve months than it=E2=
=80=99s spent.
Three years ago, Eight Sleep had low gross margins (revenue - costs of good=
s sold) and lower contribution margins (gross margins - CAC). It made a lit=
