y each customer is multiples higher than the cost to acquire that customer.=
 This number has improved as gross margin has, and as churn on Autopilot ha=
s come down.=C2=A0
Impressively, they=E2=80=99re putting together those unit economics while c=
ontinuing to grow quickly. The company is on pace to nearly double revenue =
again this year, with big growth coming from Autopilot and international.=
=C2=A0
Eight Sleep now controls its own destiny. It=E2=80=99s not going to die, un=
like thousands of consumer hardware companies that have come before it. If =
it continues doing what it=E2=80=99s doing, it should print bigger piles of=
 cash each year.=C2=A0
