The HyperPod, when it comes out, will take those advantages and turn them 3=
D. Already, the HyperPod prototype that Matteo and Alexandra sleep in can p=
roduce 3D scans of their bodies using thermal imaging and computer vision. =
The HyperPod will have more sensors, and more ways to act on the data that =
