Matteo described it as =E2=80=9Ca canopy bed like you can buy at Restoratio=
n Hardware, but you close the curtains for blackout and inside it=E2=80=99s=
 making adjustments to air temperature, quality, etc=E2=80=A6 You don=E2=80=
=99t feel it, but you can reduce oxygen by 5% and you=E2=80=99ll feel the b=
