 line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><stron=
g>Form Factor</strong><span>: the surface of a mattress is really big; it c=
an fit a ton of sensors.&#160;</span></p></li></ul><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>=
That last point in particular is what flipped me. </span><strong>Eight Slee=
p functions as a laboratory in your bedroom, one that you happily jump into=
