217;t be able to get the data they need to make the impact they want.&#160;=
</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height=
: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The hardest part, then, may actually be =
over. </span><strong>Eight Sleep has been free cash flow positive over the =
