0; trickle.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There&#8217;s a reason for th=
at: Alexandra said that Eight Sleep completely redesigned the Pod 4 over 15=
