ter tubes that easily compress under the weight of your body while maintain=
ing water flow. More flexible tubing allows for greater water density withi=
n the Cover&#8217;s tubes, which means a more comfortable heating and cooli=
ng experience. And the Cover in Pod 4 is 20% thinner than the original, mor=
e averse to punctures, and more elastic, and therefore more resistant to we=
ar from tossing and turning.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); f=
ont-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Another compl=
aint is that the </span><strong>app&#8217;s user experience isn&#8217;t up =
