ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>The idea that a mattress cover could=
 lead to a predictive healthcare platform was so outlandish that Eight Slee=
p has been able to build up advantages for a decade.</strong><span> To comp=
ete now, you&#8217;d need to build a consumer hardware company that sells m=
attress covers into hundreds of thousands of homes, something that maybe on=
ly Apple would have the scale and desire to do.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D=
"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;">There are advantages to grinding it out.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color:=
 rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">=
I write these deep dives to learn about something that is endlessly fascina=
ting to me: the interaction between business models and technology, and the=
 application of both towards solving very big problems.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">My big takeaway from studying Eight Sleep is this:&#160;</p><p st=
yle=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0 0 20px 0;"><strong>There are many paths to solving big problems, and the =
path you choose depends on the problem you&#8217;re trying to solve.</stron=
g><span>&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>In some ways, it&#8217;s e=
asier to build something really, really hard &#8211; like a </span><a href=
=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/ace998d2-f406-45bb-8422-6a86b32ad2c8?j=3D=
eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">reusable rocket</a=
><span>, </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/11920c4b-63cb-4909=
-a38b-bde95c2b3e2b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-=
6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline=
;">autonomous weapons systems</a><span>, or </span><a href=3D"https://subst=
ack.com/redirect/fbcadf07-6553-4dee-a6c8-0906c130700a?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3Qif=
Q.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">advanced nuclear reactors</a><span> &=
#8211; knowing that you will be able to sell to a small number of really bi=
g buyers like the DoD or large businesses if you pull it off. And it almost=
 seems more serious, more pure to take that approach.&#160;</span></p><p st=
yle=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0 0 20px 0;"><span>But for certain problems, selling to consumers is the on=
ly way to get what you need. </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirec=
t/57ac015f-0a92-476f-912a-d50bb644e8e1?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_Zl=
NuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-d=
ecoration: underline;">Base Power Company</a><span> is a great example: its=
 batteries need to be located next to homes to have the maximum impact on t=
he grid. Eight Sleep is another one: there&#8217;s no way to get the data i=
t needs or make the impact it wants than to do the hard work of convincing =
people to buy your product.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, =
55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That approach=
 may lead people to underestimate you. I underestimated Eight Sleep, even t=
hough I&#8217;ve slept on the Pod every night for the past couple of years.=
 But looking at where Eight Sleep sits today, and how hard it&#8217;s been =
to get to this point, I think it would be a mistake to underestimate what t=
hey can do in the future.&#160;</p><div style=3D"font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px;"><hr style=3D"background: #e6e6e6; border: none; height: 1px; mar=
gin: 32px 0; padding: 0;"></div><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-si=
ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><em>Thanks to Dan and Cla=
ude for editing, and to Matteo, Alexandra, David, and Delian for your insig=
hts! </em></p><div style=3D"font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;"><hr style=
=3D"background: #e6e6e6; border: none; height: 1px; margin: 32px 0; padding=
: 0;"></div><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That&#8217;s all for today. We&#8217;ll be ba=
ck in your inbox with a Weekly Dose on Friday. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Thanks=
